---
layout: base.njk
title: "King & Snohomish County Utility Finder | Joe Sheldon"
permalink: /utility-finder/
---

<div class="utility-finder-container">
    <div class="utility-finder-card">
        
        <header class="finder-header">
            <span class="finder-tagline">Welcome to the Neighborhood</span>
            <h1 class="finder-title">Puget Sound Utility Finder</h1>
            <p class="finder-subtitle">
                Enter your new property address to instantly map your electric, gas, water, sewer, garbage, and high-speed internet providers.
            </p>
        </header>

        <div class="search-form-block">
            <div class="autocomplete-wrapper">
                <input type="text" id="address-search-input" class="search-control" placeholder="Enter your property address..." onkeyup="handleAutocompleteDebounce()" autocomplete="off">
                <div id="autocomplete-suggestions" class="suggestions-dropdown hidden"></div>
            </div>
            <button class="search-submit-btn" onclick="triggerManualSearch()">Map Utilities</button>
        </div>

        <div id="initial-prompt-state" class="state-message-block">
            <div class="message-icon">🗺️</div>
            <h3>Ready to Map Your Address</h3>
            <p>Type your address above to view your local utility providers, direct contact portals, and setup resources.</p>
        </div>

        <div id="utility-results-board" class="results-hidden">
            
            <div class="utility-category-card">
                <div class="category-header">
                    <span class="category-icon">🔋</span>
                    <h2>Electricity & Natural Gas</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="provider-details-list">
                    <div class="provider-row" id="electric-provider-row">
                        <span class="provider-label">Electric Service</span>
                        <div class="provider-value-block">
                            <span id="electric-name" class="provider-name">-</span>
                            <a id="electric-setup-link" href="#" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="provider-action-btn">Establish Service &rarr;</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="provider-row" id="gas-provider-row">
                        <span class="provider-label">Natural Gas Service</span>
                        <div class="provider-value-block">
                            <span id="gas-name" class="provider-name">-</span>
                            <a id="gas-setup-link" href="#" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="provider-action-btn">Establish Service &rarr;</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="utility-category-card">
                <div class="category-header">
                    <span class="category-icon">💧</span>
                    <h2>Water & Sewer Infrastructure</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="provider-details-list">
                    <div class="provider-row">
                        <span class="provider-label">Water District</span>
                        <div class="provider-value-block">
                            <span id="water-name" class="provider-name">-</span>
                            <a id="water-quality-link" href="#" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="provider-action-btn">Water Quality Report &rarr;</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="provider-row">
                        <span class="provider-label">Sewer / Septic System</span>
                        <div class="provider-value-block">
                            <span id="sewer-system-type" class="provider-name">Checking configuration...</span>
                            <div class="action-btn-group">
                                <a id="sewer-map-link" href="#" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="provider-action-btn">Sewer Line Map &rarr;</a>
                                <a id="septic-records-link" href="#" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="provider-action-btn hidden">Septic Records Lookup &rarr;</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div id="capacity-charge-alert" class="embedded-resource-banner hidden">
                        <div class="banner-icon">💩</div>
                        <div class="banner-body">
                            <h4>King County Sewer Capacity Charge Applies</h4>
                            <p>This property connects to a municipal sewer system that pipes into the regional King County treatment division. Learn about the 15-year capacity fee, billing cycles, and model early payoff savings.</p>
                            <a href="/sewer-capacity/" class="banner-action-link">Open Sewer Capacity Guide &rarr;</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="utility-category-card">
                <div class="category-header">
                    <span class="category-icon">🚮</span>
                    <h2>Garbage, Recycling & Yard Waste</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="provider-details-list">
                    <div class="provider-row">
                        <span class="provider-label">Municipal Franchise Holder</span>
                        <div class="provider-value-block">
                            <span id="garbage-name" class="provider-name">City-Contracted Carrier</span>
                            <a id="garbage-setup-link" href="#" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="provider-action-btn">View Waste Guidelines &rarr;</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="utility-category-card">
                <div class="category-header">
                    <span class="category-icon">🌐</span>
                    <h2>High-Speed Internet & Broadband</h2>
                </div>
                <p class="category-lede-note">
                    Real-time internet coverage query executed via the <strong>FCC National Broadband Map API</strong> for this coordinate.
                </p>
                
                <div id="internet-loading-state" class="fcc-loader-block hidden">
                    <div class="spinner"></div>
                    <p>Querying FCC database for active broadband carriers...</p>
                </div>

                <div class="table-scroll-wrapper">
                    <table class="broadband-data-table">
                        <thead>
                            <tr>
                                <th>Service Provider</th>
                                <th>Technology</th>
                                <th>Max Download Speed</th>
                                <th>Availability Link</th>
                            </tr>
                        </thead>
                        <tbody id="broadband-providers-list">
                            </tbody>
                    </table>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>

    </div>
</div>

